<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #334155; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8fafc; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #748764 0%, #627255 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: white; }
        .content { padding: 30px; }
        .footer { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; }
        .order-summary { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
        .order-summary th { text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 10px; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .order-summary td { padding: 12px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
        .total-row { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #1e293b; }
        .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .badge-success { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: #627255; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.75rem;">Thank you for your order!</h1>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0; opacity: 0.9;">Your order #{{ commande.id }} is confirmed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{ user.firstName }},</p>
            <p>We have received your order and we are starting to prepare it with care. Here is a summary of your purchases:</p>

            <table class="order-summary">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Product</th>
                        <th style="text-align: center;">Qty</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Price</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for item in commande.itemsDetails %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div style="font-weight: 600;">{{ item.name }}</div>
                            </td>
                            <td style="text-align: center;">{{ item.quantity }}</td>
                            <td style="text-align: right;">{{ item.total_price|number_format(2) }} TND</td>
                        </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                    <tr class="total-row">
                        <td colspan="2" style="padding-top: 20px;">Total</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right; padding-top: 20px;">{{ commande.totalAmount|number_format(2) }} TND</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px;">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase;">Shipping Information</h3>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Address:</strong> {{ commande.shippingAddress }}</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Phone:</strong> {{ commande.contactPhone }}</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Payment:</strong> 
                    <span class="badge badge-success">
                        {{ commande.paymentMethod|replace({'_': ' '})|capitalize }}
                    </span>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="#" class="btn">Track my order</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Slimenify - Well-being & Recovery Platform</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
